{"tid":1021493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱喺地鐵見到有個呀叔好似想抽人水","createTime":"2019-02-14T09:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T10:01:50.000Z","uid":167330,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1403df4098b56a0dcb12a75c8bfb941f4dc7336e","tid":1021493,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"當時地鐵好逼，個呀叔背脊逼到個女人個胸好貼，睇年紀一定唔係情侶，而且佢哋都冇交流，唔似係誏嘅。我見個女人遮住個胸，好似好辛苦咁，於是下意識覺得個呀叔應該係逼得佢太實，而且唔排除係特登想抽水，因為明明佢前面仲有少少位<br />\n<br />\n於是我就拍咗一拍個呀叔，同佢講：「先生，不如你企前少少，後面有人。」 之後佢就向前行咗少少，之後我繼續上連登，但我瞄到個呀叔好似一直怒啤住我。好似想打鳩我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後個女人同我講咗一句野，我估係講唔該，但問題嚟喇，我全程戴住耳機，完全聽唔到佢講乜，亦唔知個呀叔有冇講過野。<br />\n<br />\n我唔排除佢哋係識嘅，但我觀察所得佢哋係唔識嘅，又或者如果個女人其實根本冇俾佢逼到，只係我角度問題，咁我咪柒咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我係咪做多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係我誤會咗，我喺度同當事人道個歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你見到嘅話<br />\n<br />\n不過我寧願係誤會，自己柒咗，都好過真係有人想抽水而唔阻止，但希望我唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人當時見到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 荃灣線"},{"pid":"8bea7e03440fb8a77fd7112e8a9ad927afad2b82","tid":1021493,"uid":63870,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"我係隔離，個女仔話想請你食飯"},{"pid":"f4822319dd65d0327c6d43c55ba24b31409d5083","tid":1021493,"uid":44607,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"做得好 柒左好小事 總好過睇住個呀叔抽水唔幫口"},{"pid":"a47b583e710186b879a5042eea4bcc852337991c","tid":1021493,"uid":167330,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8bea7e03440fb8a77fd7112e8a9ad927afad2b82","tid":1021493,"uid":63870,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"我係隔離，個女仔話想請你食飯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"你俾人隔離咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70697f646f98ecb99243a8a9c412af2f336347c7","tid":1021493,"uid":220701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"99eea1b5e63218c3667f52c2f42cb9528e6ac5f8","tid":1021493,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4822319dd65d0327c6d43c55ba24b31409d5083","tid":1021493,"uid":44607,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"做得好 柒左好小事 總好過睇住個呀叔抽水唔幫口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"聽到呢句個心舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌，好想知個女人究竟同我講咗啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48457d9d57a71b5a587fced37d66e42e59fdf737","tid":1021493,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99eea1b5e63218c3667f52c2f42cb9528e6ac5f8","tid":1021493,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4822319dd65d0327c6d43c55ba24b31409d5083","tid":1021493,"uid":44607,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"做得好 柒左好小事 總好過睇住個呀叔抽水唔幫口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"聽到呢句個心舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌，好想知個女人究竟同我講咗啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"想同你食餐飯"},{"pid":"dce12626d12988219427cb6cb42a90e90eccd832","tid":1021493,"uid":231980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"唔該晒你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3730ba28c5fa1209709cda46051dde9964d005","tid":1021493,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"會唔會你以為同你講多謝，實際係講多事"},{"pid":"f59015d24bd7ead5343f5bfe8ea5b24bfdddbed2","tid":1021493,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,